1. Instruction
For the neutron detector research, type:
make -f GNUmakefile_neutron

For the researches not using the neutron detector, type:
make

2. Remark
When compliling for the neutron detector research, it uses DMXPhysicsList.
The other case uses A01PhysicsList.

3. This directory is modified with Source code
(LAMPSDetectorConstruction.cc, SiCsI is removed)
